name: IncomeShares S&P 500 Options (0DTE) ETP
description_en: The IncomeShares S&P 500 Options (0DTE) ETP is an actively managed ETF. The ETP strategy is to provide exposure to the S&P 500 and sell put options on the S&P 500 index or the SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust to generate premia. The ETN's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.45% p.a.. The dividends in the ETN are distributed to the investors (Monthly). The IncomeShares S&P 500 Options (0DTE) ETP is a very small ETN with 6m Euro assets under management. The ETN was launched on 27 August 2024 and is domiciled in Ireland.
description_cs: Možnosti INCOMESHARES S&P 500 (0DTE) ETP je aktivně spravovaná ETF. Strategií ETP je poskytnout expozici S&P 500 a prodat opce na put na index S&P 500 nebo SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust pro generování prémií. TER ETN (celkový poměr nákladů) činí 0,45% p.a. dividenday v ETN jsou distribuovány investorům (měsíčně). Incomeshares S&P 500 Options (0DTE) ETP je velmi malý ETN s managementem 6m euro. ETN byl spuštěn 27. srpna 2024 a je se sídlem v Irsku.

name: KraneShares Global Carbon Strategy ETC
description_en: The KraneShares Global Carbon Strategy ETC seeks to track the S&P Global Carbon Credit index. The S&P Global Carbon Credit index tracks the price of futures contracts on carbon allowances. The ETC's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.78% p.a.. The KraneShares Global Carbon Strategy ETC is the only ETC that tracks the S&P Global Carbon Credit index. The ETC replicates the performance of the underlying index with a collateralised debt obligation which is backed by physical holdings of the precious metal. The KraneShares Global Carbon Strategy ETC is a very small ETC with 8m Euro assets under management. The ETC was launched on 3 October 2024 and is domiciled in Ireland.

name: WisdomTree STOXX Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short
description_en: The WisdomTree STOXX Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short seeks to track the STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense Short Leverage (-3x) index. The STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense Short Leverage (-3x) index tracks the three times leveraged inverse performance of the STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense index on a daily basis. The STOXX Europe Total Market Aerospace & Defense index tracks the performance of European companies that are engaged in the aerospace and defense industry. The ETN's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.85% p.a.. The ETN replicates the performance of the underlying index synthetically with a swap. The dividends in the ETN are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The WisdomTree STOXX Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short is a very small ETN with 1m Euro assets under management. The ETN was launched on 23 April 2025 and is domiciled in Ireland.
description_cs: WisdomTree Stoxx Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short se snaží sledovat index Stoxx Europe Aerospace & Defence Short Leafed (-3x). Index Stoxx Europe Europe Aerospace & Defense Short Leavel (-3x) sleduje třikrát využívaný inverzní výkon celkového trhu Stoxx Europe Aerospace & Defense Index. Index Aerospace & Defense Stoxx Europe Celkový trh sleduje výkon evropských společností, které se zabývají leteckým a obranným průmyslem. ETN TER (celkový poměr nákladů) činí 0,85% p.a. ETN replikuje výkon podkladového indexu synteticky s výměnou. dividenday v ETN jsou akumulovány a reinvestovány do ETF. WisdomTree Stoxx Europe Aerospace & Defense 3x Daily Short je velmi malý ETN s 1m euro ve spravování. ETN byl spuštěn 23. dubna 2025 a je se sídlem v Irsku.

name: WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity Carry
description_en: The WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity Carry seeks to track the BNP Paribas Enhanced Commodity Carry Excess Return index. Der BNP Paribas Enhanced Commodity Carry Excess Return index provides exposure to a leveraged premium (also known as the commodity carry factor) from the difference in the carry costs between the long and short positions in futures contracts of the same set of underlying commodities. The ETC's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.40% p.a.. The WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity Carry is the only ETC that tracks the BNP Paribas Enhanced Commodity Carry Excess Return index. The ETC replicates the performance of the underlying index synthetically with a swap. The WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity Carry is a small ETC with 69m Euro assets under management. The ETC was launched on 24 April 2025 and is domiciled in Ireland.
description_cs: WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity Carry se snaží sledovat BNP Paribas Enhanced Commodity Index nadbytečné návratnosti. Der BNP Paribas Enhenced Commodity Commodity Commodity Commodity Commodity Recess Return Index poskytuje expozici pákovému prémii (také známému jako komoditní přepravní faktor) z rozdílu v nákladech na přepravu mezi dlouhými a krátkými pozicemi v futures kontraktu stejného souboru základních komodit. Ter (celkový poměr nákladů) ETC činí 0,40% p.a. ETC replikuje výkon podkladového indexu synteticky s výměnou. WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity Carry je malá atd. S managementem 69 milionů euro. ETC bylo zahájeno 24. dubna 2025 a je v Irsku bydliště.
